Check is just a simple tester function.  To use format the email as following then encrypt it.(For more infomation about encrypted send an email back with 'help GPG' in the subject line.

email:(the email address you sent the this email from.)
command:check
user:(The username you registred with (Does accept random string here) )
password:(The password you registed with (Does accept random string here) )
[start]
(Put whatever you want here.  As it really doesn't matter)
[end]
